Ok, now the Bus!!!!!!!!!!! ggggrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrRRRRRRRRR
Am 20 miles north of san diego right now on a small state beach park on the 
ocean.
Here is my 3 main problem in order(S)
- Tranny problem, pretty sure it's the bushing in front of the tranny, 2 
