-Carbs!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! Running to rich at idle like hell!!! i think my fuel 
pump is giving to much pressure (flooded each morning and near impossible to 
start, in the morning the engine is always flooded)
and very dificult to start. I have a 100$ electric fuel pump (with 
regulator) but i had no time to install this one! INEED NEW CARBS, or very 
good use one, i would also settle for single weber! I had to put my spare 
carbs yesterday, they are fine on freeway but TOOOOOO much ritch for driving 
in town!!!! they smell like hell when am at a stop or at idle! I am tired of 
those carbs, iv'e been playing with those all my way down south! changing 
jets (air and fuel), the other one completely failed in....Arizona, i could 
do nothing with those!
Some morning or simply after fuelling the bus, black puff smoke, heavy 
hesitation, impossible to drive, light smell in the van at night when we are 
speeping!!!

I am simply dead, driving more than 500 mile some days, my girl didn't dive 
